  "last_full_audit": "2026-05-01",
  "methodology": "Enumerate app/**/*.py and alembic/**/*.py in cueapi-core; include every file whose same-path counterpart exists in the private cueapi clone at audit time. Files that are OSS-only (no private counterpart) are intentionally excluded — modifications to them do not need a parity cross-reference.",
